lic elements are correctly set. I wonder if I should also remove any extra blank lines before closing. It might satisfy the checkstyle, even though it feels not entirely important. But still, I think it's a good habit to maintain clean formatting. Let's see how it looks once those adjustments are made!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e6ab983e6cb0a45016a26b8ff98d48194a41d84ca98bb6806\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJrkUlF3Hv6sHXHNi7nrd6gWrDBroqZk8OtHdu-UKamSXivPQbVz5SQto7MejF2AmvblPVlqkP39YTKTYRGMBGb_C9OEj0hMds4l3Pn8dTAGW5bdkciA9rbwcOZllAdf5Z6WXCKa-niyhF0EbGMh642dH4qB5YhoGBVkUo_0l34fV_fi29TSlMYx1i8z9W_61zkS_oXSWgZDAmZPd1HLMZ7Gflu9OtgfqIL9mj-TtkqbM9SH1Bx7gSZFZu3Ge52YTXD5S6v-m-rN9oo7EXaT9Q_0VBbixeMVHnibxbeDnGaw9YFPLSwyCKXrhfPbfgnQt5WXx4TwCDo8six-oXa1tVXtVvvRKGjOqYQ6M9HPvKbDojjVdiucFtuv64pkjwUj10oAHbG3KXFqrb32btcffYHF6RSU-uxr5qqGLU8nna325rrUJU4Ol1UT_TZMt7A_aqNvwd0HLApfIDFlACgqkwkKKJHjYbISYqerD7XdFTdnww-2WIFPgDU5HmIGWhCW8l9a8uKPnaF03PPwqvAqOvmFcGqA_pB1VysKI0ocj0l1sjwZwFU4epfneZcVAq1_LJL2BPV4e74nS9cHJKEN_8vPKVNu8BhfxJfj-x14vNlPcnsdCyAUCgK5J0I2rlQtrAZkEwYfVZT_5Nh2HRk6Hu1o51mJuYWz-lOMaHw9Ti_1qftLWlruj8GJIxgjAOSp_5s6N3qPbJF9AwglKFgd0Gki3-lpe8NVCUFh-0doZ0wvRNZMzO7xY_LhV0OlveDcy1LprR_Yqon_IEcM4ChVcABIXZoqJEHzsGGQlhRWngenjDXc8_2uMQ4N7NG-fHZH-sdbHlYUsRN599_G5MKrEujyb-qBcUwUe0g_Mazz0xYZg1bPYfn6bB7VXC2fKYf9QCV9VgWFL0QjHiOXWMQclzQxvwNuPV15B44W7DD1QhBsDCwxZW1tMKFpUDaAlSwTk-X9vldAZE0d7XL6qDtoV_NP3e5hAP6mpO6GuZD-speD6Yb6ACY4vZOBavvSE6euq-iPLq0P0B07GnThmfoi6vEHc9x4pYwlHhiZ-GdKu9Z_DLvDOEps0szD6B9AKxuKfIJZP6nN3pmMW2l3-0nP5Jp1RoldwHdkJ-uNY653Btnb7pSkf48Q6VbWuC6FflzTXf41zU89MgPR8PwWHh6tZOJWzU7E1i6FWXwdMo1jAFsU3Kogh4tH1XFwD7YWcoc2sFicdLYTktGmjWqvMxe7J453Rvx6NpJZYgTYsA5rbNECUkE8KpKCUL3U6sx7covGxO5hvxESZnycmZ2aYCakeLQyHMa1lvn5RG_XmYZzZZU_zLSjn1FTAOmifjsw5pU06V15unDAEMai4dNs2Cbwz6AV2Z4OzSKl21JIROvwRJK75HQs6Se6ot6UujE1ZEemeCzxPFCN1D0hNSnh-F0OvNbOk3SJ0aBJVdfqNoLB7ZRjXgK5nmDGMKpc8_krU5Fn_xSSYz55eNFq9Na_OFxvFRgg67CN9PqaGH58SQosfLAObA9Ar3lbRYQTk-zmfktM0